---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Create a term

Usage: mf term new [OPTIONS] <TERM>

Arguments:
  <TERM>  

Options:
      --definition <DEFINITION>  
      --root <PATH>              
      --alias <ALIAS>            
      --config <PATH>            
      --tag <TAG>                
  -v, --verbose...               
      --project <PROJECT>        
  -q, --quiet                    
      --format <FORMAT>          [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color                 
  -h, --help                     Print help
  -V, --version                  Print version
